MESSAGE: this is the most unique; eye catching; and thrilling rav4 you will ever see. sports car like handling; but still a fully capable 4wd suv. modifications are the 18 tsw lightweight forged wheels with michelin pilot super sports 245/40. the 2gr-fe motor found in this toyota is the same motor found in the lotus evora/exige so it is no slouch either... over 280 hp in a vehicle that weighs only 3500 pounds. those are luxury sports sedan numbers. this sport rav4 came with bilstein shocks from the factory so i just paired them up with h&r lowering springs. ride height is perfect. ive yet to bottom out or curb anything. feels rally capable! it is truly an incredible drive youd have to experience to believe. it is a stiffer ride to be expected compared to other suvs; but the shocks do absorb the bumps nicely. has a fully custom 2.5 inch borla dual exhaust w/x-pipe and high flow catalytic converters; sounds absolutely fantastic. a real neck breaker because the sound makes you think an exotic car is driving by. has a short ram style intake with an afe filter connected to tubing stretching to the front grille for grabbing the coldest air. comes with the factory 18 sport gunmetal/machined wheels with winter tires 245/45. spent over 2;000 dollars on the oem rav4 ev led headlights. you will not see another rav4 with them. toyota reliability at its finest. ive never had any problems. practical and fun daily driver.
